#: ../../campaigns/campaign_builder.rst:26 caec0526e9a54a758760df041335e91f
msgid ""
"**Contact Forms**: choose this option if you want to start the Campaign when"
" the Contact completes a specified Form. Forms are the primary point of "
"gathering information about a Contact. It's possible to take action in a "
"Campaign based on the Form field values submitted."
